# Guest layer (`src/app/guest`)

Public / unauthenticated area. No sidebar — `GuestShellComponent` (topbar + scrollable outlet + optional footer).

## Routes (`guest.routes.ts`)

Two `GuestShellComponent` trees: root (`/`, `/sign-in`, `/login`, `/register`) and `admin` prefix (`/admin/login`).

| Path | Page | Guard | Notes |
|------|------|-------|-------|
| `/` | `LandingPageComponent` | `guestGuard` | `data: { showFooter: true, showNavActions: true }` |
| `/sign-in` | `SignInPageComponent` | `guestGuard` | Portal picker cards; `data: { showNavActions: true }` |
| `/login` | `UserLoginPageComponent` | `guestGuard` | User login |
| `/admin/login` | `AdminLoginPageComponent` | `guestGuard` | Admin login |
| `/register` | `RegisterCompanyPageComponent` | `guestGuard` | Company registration |

## Shell (`guest/shell/`)

- `GuestShellComponent` — reads deepest route `data.showFooter` / `data.showNavActions`
- `GuestTopbarComponent` — brand, language/theme pickers (`shared/ui/`), conditional nav actions
- `GuestFooterComponent` — landing footer links
- `PortalCardComponent` — user/admin portal cards on sign-in page

## Pages (`guest/pages/`)

- `landing/` — marketing hero + feature cards
- `sign-in/` — portal picker (login URLs from `shared/constants/app-urls.ts`)
- `login/` — split pages (`user-login-page`, `admin-login-page`); shared `login.form.ts`, `login.model.ts`, `login-page.component.scss`; accent via `.login--user` / `.login--admin` on page root
- `register/` — company registration stepper (`mode: 'stepper'`): `register-company-page`, `register-company.form.ts`, `register-company.model.ts`, `register-company.service.ts` (stub), `register-company.config.ts` (API path), `register-company.constants.ts` (select options). Create-only — no `stepperMode` / `stepperDataReady` bindings; see `forms.mdc`.

## Constants & imports

- App URLs: `shared/constants/guest-urls.ts` (`LANDING_URL`, login/register paths); import via `app-urls.ts` barrel (`portalHomeUrl()` lives there)
- Auth: `shared/core/auth/auth.service.ts`
- Guest imports `shared/**` only — do **not** import portal configs, features, or shell
